Author information:
(1)Dutch CF Foundation, Dr. A. Schweitzerweg 3a, 3744 MG Baarn, the Netherlands.
(2)Radboudumc Center for Infectious Diseases, Dept. of Medical Microbiology, 
Radboud University Medical Center, Nijmegen, the Netherlands. Electronic 
