(8)Dept. of Respiratory Medicine, Maastricht University Medical Center+, 
Maastricht, the Netherlands.
(9)Dutch CF Foundation, Baarn, the Netherlands.
(10)Dept. of Pulmonology, University Medical Centre Utrecht, the Netherlands.
(11)Sophia Children's Hospital, Department of Pediatrics, Erasmus University 
